{
  "stem": "21582.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I mean, my father kind of, you know, worked, and-- which was all very clandestine.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we-- no, and the rest-- we tried to keep it as normal as we could.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Within our family, our home, our family was like a little capsule, like-- like a little safe haven.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, I have these images with the flickering carbide, where everything was dark.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The windows were blacked out, and the silence-- the silence beyond our walls were deafening.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because, you know, we listened to the silence, because it often-- there were clues.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Survival depended on alertness.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So you always listened to the silence, if anything would erupt.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But in our-- I remember our kitchen, we would sit, of course, only at one place, because you could only keep one place warm, if you had enough fuel.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we had the carbide light.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my father would read.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He read to us a lot-- [HEBREW] and Sholem Aleichem and Sholem Asch.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he just brought back the images of-- of a world that-- that fed us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But outside, outside the quiet and the threat always hung.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Now, our-- our apartment, our windows were directly across the-- across the courtyard from the gate.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Now, it was my sister's and my job to often watch if the-- because you never knew where the Germans would just spring out from nowhere.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And so it was sort of our job to watch if the Germans were coming into the building.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was also all the children's job when we were playing outside to keep-- nobody told us, but we were part of the family.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "My parents-- all the discussions and everything was shared, and we knew where things were hidden and everything.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were treated as kindly as they possibly could.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
